reviewText:
All the things that you'd want in a game

Dead Population ✔
Non-existant English (And only in the launcher) ✔
Completely Chinese in-game ✔
Controls like complete garbage ✔

tl;dr Don't let the graphics and art style fool you, while the character design is pretty neat imo, you'd have more fun playing the most pay to win f2p game on steam.
